text: The 2015 Canada Open Grand Prix was the eighth grand prix and grand prix gold tournament of the 2015 BWF Grand Prix and Grand Prix Gold. The tournament was held at the Markin MacPhail Centre in Calgary, Canada June 23 until June 28, 2015 and had a total purse of $50,000. ==Players by nation== {| class="wikitable sortable" style="text-align: center; width:500px " |- !Nation!!
